dc_title_s: France--north coast, approaches to Dieppe (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: modified facsimile copy of French chart 5927, 5th edition 1984, corrected through 1988. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From survey of SHOM and léquipment to 1983." "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Soundings in meters." Includes origin of hydrographic information diagram and tidal tables. Map NO.37111 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. Service hydrographique et océanographique de la marine. Defense Mapping Agency
